# lcod://tooling/object/entries@0.1.0

Return an object's entries as [key, value] pairs.

## Inputs

| Name | Type | Required | Description |
| --- | --- | --- | --- |
| `value` | object | null | No | Object whose entries should be enumerated. |

## Outputs

| Name | Type | Description |
| --- | --- | --- |
| `entries` | array<array<any>> | Array of [key, value] pairs. |
